Package: mditre
Type: Package
Title: Microbiome Differentiable Interpretable Temporal Rule Engine
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2025-11-02
Authors@R: c(
    person("MDITRE", "Development Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mditre@example.com")
    )
Description: MDITRE is a deep learning framework for analyzing longitudinal 
    microbiome time-series data. It implements a 5-layer fully differentiable 
    neural network architecture that learns human-interpretable rules combining 
    phylogenetic relationships and temporal dynamics. This R implementation 
    provides integration with phyloseq and the Bioconductor ecosystem.
